attributionInfo.agentName: Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection
Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection

description: Nestled in the heart of South Boston near Thomas Park, this stunning 4-bed, 3.5-bath single-family home blends classic charm with modern convenience. The inviting foyer opens to a sun-filled, open-concept living area with hardwood floors and a cozy gas fireplace, perfect for gatherings.  The chef’s kitchen features subway tile, GE appliances, a quartz island, pantry, and coffee bar. Enjoy your private fenced backyard for relaxing or entertaining.  Upstairs, three spacious bedrooms offer retreats, along with a shared full bath and laundry closet. The luxurious primary suite includes an en-suite bath, walk-in closet, and bow front windows. The top floor serves as an additional bedroom, kids’ playroom, or office with an en-suite bath.  Ideal for families and professionals, this home offers the best of South Boston living in a prime location.
